N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7202.2 - Definitions

State Regulations
(a) Data subject
shall mean any natural person about whom personal information has been
collected by the commission. (b) Personal information shall mean any information concerning a data subject
which, because of name, number, symbol, mark or other identification, can be
used to identify that data subject. Notes
